comment_data.body: Thanks for the report. I assume you were using Cython 0.27? I have no idea why that would happen as pickling is even explicitly supported for that class. But since there was a bit of duplication, I committed a little change, may or may not have an impact. Could you retry with latest master?

Sorry, seems like I was trying to install old version. 2.3 or something.
New one is working fine.
